---

---

<section class="py-24 bg-white border-t border-gray-100">
    <!-- Top Half (The Manifesto) -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2
            class="text-4xl font-extrabold sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl tracking-tight mb-8 text-gray-900"
        >
            The Profit Engine
        </h2>
        <div
            class="prose prose-lg mx-auto text-gray-600 text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed text-left sm:text-center"
        >
            <p class="mb-6">
                Most agencies look like geniuses when ads are cheap. But the era
                of cheap clicks is dead. Now, the bad marketers are exposed.
                When growth stops, they panic. They jump to cheap tricks. They
                buy fake metrics. They make sales at a massive loss just to show
                you a positive graph.
            </p>
            <p>
                Any fool can spend a dollar to make ninety cents. I build
                systems engineered for pure profit. The standard agency model
                has a massive gap in accountability. They get paid to spend your
                budget. I operate differently. When I build your machine, we
                follow four strict rules.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bottom Half (The Grid) -->
    <div class="mt-20 max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
            <!-- Item 1 -->
            <div
                class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M15 12a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path>
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M2.458 12C3.732 7.943 7.523 5 12 5c4.478 0 8.268 2.943 9.542 7-1.274 4.057-5.064 7-9.542 7-4.477 0-8.268-2.943-9.542-7z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                    1. Your customer does not care about you.
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    They only care about their own problems. We strip the ego
                    out of your marketing. We look at the market exactly how
                    your buyer sees it.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 2 -->
            <div
                class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M11 5.882V19.24a1.76 1.76 0 01-3.417.592l-2.147-6.15M18 13a3 3 0 100-6M5.436 13.683A4.001 4.001 0 017 6h1.832c4.1 0 7.625-1.234 9.168-3v14c-1.543-1.766-5.067-3-9.168-3H7a3.988 3.988 0 01-1.564-.317z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                    2. Overkill is the baseline.
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    Because buyers do not care about you, you must be impossible
                    to ignore. You have to be loud. You have to be relentlessly
                    consistent. We make your message unavoidable.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 3 -->
            <div
                class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M9.663 17h4.673M12 3v1m6.364 1.636l-.707.707M21 12h-1M4 12H3m3.343-5.657l-.707-.707m2.828 9.9a5 5 0 117.072 0l-.548.547A3.374 3.374 0 0014 18.469V19a2 2 0 11-4 0v-.531c0-.895-.356-1.754-.988-2.386l-.548-.547z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                    3. The remembered brand gets the money.
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    If a buyer does not think of you the exact second a problem
                    hits, you lose. We build systems that put you in their head
                    long before they reach for their wallet.
                </p>
            </div>

            <!-- Item 4 -->
            <div
                class="bg-gray-50 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-100 shadow-sm transition-all hover:shadow-md"
            >
                <div
                    class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-teal-600 mb-6"
                >
                    <svg
                        class="w-6 h-6"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3">
                    4. Own the search. Predict the future.
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed text-lg">
                    We track exactly how often people look for you versus the
                    competition. This data acts like a canary in the coal mine.
                    It lets us predict market shifts before they happen. If you
                    own the search demand, you own the market.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
